features: 【5pcs Durable and Comfortable Bag Set 】: 5 pcs weekend overnight bag design including 1 duffel bag , 1 cosmetic bag, 1 crossbody bag and 2 shoe bags. Perfect for carrying all your fitness and travel essentials. It can be used as an airplane travel bag, duffel bag, gym sports bag, weekend bag, carry-on bag, beach bag.

【Multi-compartments Gym Bag 】: The large capacity gym bag has 1 spacious main compartment and 2 interiors (1 laptop compartment and 1 large zippered wet bag) making it easy to organize and pack your clothes, cosmetics, iPad, snacks, and more. It also features 2 side pockets for your water bottle and umbrella, and two easy-access exterior pockets: a front pocket for earbuds, and a zippered back pocket for keeping your keys, cash, cards, and other valuables safe.

【Airplane Friendly Carry on Bag】: Dimensions: 18.5’’x14.2’’x9”. This external rechargeable travel bag is designed to support you on any journey including weekend getaways, domestic/ international flights, and cruises. You can carry it as a personal item on flight and it perfectly fits under the seat for airlines such as Spirit, Jet Blue, and AA. The trolley sleeve perfectly secures any suitcase for easy carrying during the trip.

【Dry Wet Separated Gym Bag & Separated Shoe Compartment 】: With this travel gym bag designed for women, you'll have plenty of room to store your belongings. You can keep your wet clothes, shower essentials, and gym towels separate from other items with the zippered waterproof PVC-lined pocket. In addition, the bottom of the bag features a separate waterproof shoe compartment for two pairs of shoes(two additional shoe bags are provided). There are two air vents to disperse the bad smell of shoes, and a large mesh compartment for storing socks.

【After-sales service】Our products are 100% quality inspected before they are delivered to you, If you find any zipper damage or other quality problems after receiving the product, please contact ours customer service for free return/refund service.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute and spacious
reviews.reviewText: I use this as weekend or short trip bag. I really like the space at the bottom of the bag where you can put your shoes or makeup stuff. There’s many places to organize your things for traveling.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Beautiful, durable, well made....this is truly a quality product for the price. Everyone should own one!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars No need for a suitcase! This fits all
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I didn’t expect this bag to fit in as much as it did. I didn’t want to buy and carry a large expensive suitcase all while id be travelling and this was perfect to carry and organize my clothes, shoes, accessories, and etc. theres plenty of space provided as well as extra bags inside. I love the shoe compartment as well. Not to mention it looks so stylish to carry around and is all around something I recommend to anyone traveling and wanting a better, convenient, and elevated way of organizing their necessities. So classy , love it. Promoting this on my content for sure.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars An amazing bag. First review I’ve ever made
reviews.reviewText: I’m not kidding when I tell you I have never written a review for anything and I have over 900 purchases. This bag fit all of my essentials. I put my makeup bag, travel toiletries. 3 pairs of shoes, an extra outfit, snacks and a my iPad. And there was more room. I didn’t even realize it came with an extra little purse with a long cross body strap. It fit perfectly under my United seat but I put it up because I needed to stretch my legs. But you couldn’t see the bag under the seat.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 31, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I like this bag but the size is deceiving with the zippered area below. It doesn't leave a lot of room in the top area as expected it would. I love the crossbody bag that came with this tote. Put my wallet, phone and lipstick in it for going out for dinner while in vacation. The cosmetic bag is also good size. Next time I pack it I will use the lower section for something other than shoes. I shortened the tab on the pocket that's for a tablet. It was way to long letting the pocket fall open and in the way.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I love it, its the best, I have so much room in the bag and you get lots of bags with it

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best gift for a busy person.
reviews.reviewText: This bag is so versatile. Laptop in one compartment, clothes in the other, and shoes in the very bottom zipper. Great for a busy body that is always in the go and very pretty with good quality!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: If you’re thinking about it. Just buy it. It’s amazing. I was traveling and had two layovers so I prepared this bag with everything I might need for my kids for the plane plus each stop. Let’s just say I still had plenty of space even after packing a change of clothes for each, toys, iPads, lunch box, snacks, blankets, pretty much anything you can think of I put in this bag.I did not use the charge port, or the storage bags for the shoes. However the quality of the shoe bags seem good and the additional storage bags are the same material as the bag itself which is very nice and durable.Again if you’re thinking about it. Just buy it!
